title: Bug 7945: Search results not selected in external jar
description: Bug 7945: Search results not selected in external jar Build 200201151. Search for references to this field5.
OB: When searching for references to a specific field in the external jar, the search results are not being selected.
EB: You should get 3 matches in the method getTempDir() when searching for references to this field6.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:

1. Open the external jar in the IDE.
2. Perform a search for references to the specific field.
3. Observe that the search results are not being selected correctly.
